<h5 id="switchable-normalization-layer" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#switchable-normalization-layer"><span>Switchable Normalization Layer</span></a></h5>
<blockquote>
<p>前三者的结合，提出自适配归一化方法，自动为神经网络中每个归一化曾确定合适的归一化操作</p>
<p>SN = BN + IN + LN</p>
</blockquote>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213201228993.png" alt="image-20241213201228993" style="zoom:67%;" />
$$
\hat{h}_{ncij}=\gamma\frac{h_{ncij}-\Sigma_{k\in\Omega}w_k\mu_k}{\sqrt{\Sigma_{k\in\Omega}w_k^{\prime}\sigma_k^2+\epsilon}}+\beta,
$$
