lass="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<h5 id="通道数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#通道数"><span>通道数</span></a></h5>
<p><code v-pre>通道方向有多个特征图时，按通道进行输入数据和卷积核的卷积核运算，将结果相加得到输出</code></p>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240925210101774.png" alt="image-20240925210101774" style="zoom:67%;" />
<h4 id="卷积次数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#卷积次数"><span>卷积次数</span></a></h4>
<blockquote>
<p>卷积次数要多层，多次卷积后，特征图单像素的感受野逐渐增大，观察视野从局部到全局</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="感受野" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#感受野"><span>感受野</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>输出特征图上某个元素受输入图像上影响的区域</code></p>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/5f42b016089be4a9f705afd88ab822ea.png" alt="img" style="zoom: 67%;" />
<h4 id="批处理" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#批处理"><span>批处理</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>各层间的传递数据保存为4维数据（batch_num,channel,height,width）</code></p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240925211607463.png" alt="image-20240925211607463" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20240925211607463</figcaption></figure>
<h3 id="池化层" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#池化层"><span>池化层</span></a></h3>
<p><code v-pre>使用数据压缩，在减小计算量的同时防止过拟合</code></p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Max池化：计算目标区域的最大值</li>
<li>Average池化：计算目标区域的平均值（不常用）</li>
</ul>
<p>一般来讲，池化的窗口大小会和步幅设定为相同值</p>
</blockquote>
<p>池化层特征：</p>
<ol>
<li>不学习的参数【只是从目标区域取最大值（或平均值），不存在要学习的参数】</li>
<li>通道数不发生变化【按照通道减小数据】</li>
<li>对微小的位置变化具有健壮性【平移不变性、旋转不变性、尺度不变性】
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240925213812074.png" alt="image-20240925213812074" style="zoom: 33%;" /></li>
</ol>
<p>池化过程：</p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240925215841772.png" alt="image-20240925215841772" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20240925215841772</figcaption></figure>
<h3 id="卷积核变化可视化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#卷积核变化可视化"><span>卷积核变化可视化</span></a></h3>
<blockquote>
<p>卷积核在做什么？观察边缘（颜色变化的分界线）和斑块（局部的块状区域）</p>
<p>随着层次加深，提取的信息越来越抽象，神经元从简单的形状向“高级”信息变化</p>
</blockquote>
<p>卷积层权重示意图：</p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240926093615857.png" alt="image-20240926093615857" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20240926093615857</figcaption></figure>
<p>卷积层权重示意图：</p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240926093806417.png" alt="image-20240926093806417" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20240926093806417</figcaption></figure>
<h3 id="特征图可视化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#特征图可视化"><span>特征图可视化</span></a></h3>
<p>卷积+激活+卷积2+激活2：</p>
<p><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241215151742176.png" alt="image-20241215151742176" style="zoom:67%;" /><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241226152330722.png" alt="image-20241226152330722" style="zoom:67%;" /><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241226152409925.png" alt="image-20241226152409925" style="zoom:67%;" /><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241226152419491.png" alt="image-20241226152419491" style="zoom:67%;" /></p>
<p>池化后：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>经过池化，可以明显的发现局部信息提亮了</p>
</blockquote>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241226152430411.png" alt="image-20241226152430411" style="zoom:67%;" />
<p>经过多个卷积层的feature map：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>可以看出，难以解释</p>
</blockquote>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241215152246267.png" alt="image-20241215152246267" style="zoom:67%;" />
<h3 id="经典卷积网络" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#经典卷积网络"><span>经典卷积网络</span></a></h3>
<blockquote>
<p>问：为什么卷积几次才池化一次？</p>
<p>答案：需要累积特征</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="lenet" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#lenet"><span>LeNet</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>最早用于数字识别的CNN</code></p>
<p>图为LeNet-5：</p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240926094851231.png" alt="image-20240926094851231" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>image-20240926094851231</figcaption></figure>
<ol>
<li>激活函数：sigmoid</li>
<li>池化层：subsampling</li>
</ol>
<p>当前流行的CNN：</p>
<ol>
<li>激活函数：ReLU（-1~1更大的范围）</li>
<li>池化层：Max池化（增强特征）</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="alexnet" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#alexnet"><span>AlexNet</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>2012年ILSVRC比赛冠军，远超第二名的CNN，比LeNet更深，用多层小卷积叠加来替换单个的大卷积</code></p>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/dbcbcc632ea823bc331e7fae8d2790ff-1727403602440-3.png" alt="dbcbcc632ea823bc331e7fae8d2790ff" style="zoom:80%;" />
<ol>
<li>激活函数：ReLU</li>
<li>池化：Max池化</li>
<li>使用局部正规化层【LRN（Local Response Normalization）】</li>
<li>使用Dropout</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="zf-net" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#zf-net"><span>ZF Net</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>2013年ILSVRC比赛冠军</code></p>
<h4 id="vgg" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#vgg"><span>Vgg</span></a></h4>
<blockquote>
<p>做完池化之后特征减少，马上使用卷积补特征</p>
</blockquote>
<img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/1233445.png" style="zoom: 50%;" />
<h4 id="resnet" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#resnet"><span>Resnet</span></a></h4>
<p><code v-pre>残差神经网络：模型训练过程至少不比原来差</code></p>
<p>网络层数越多误差越大？？？</p>
<figure><img src="@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/v2-dcf5688dad675cbe8fb8be243af5e1fd_r.jpg" alt="img" tabindex="0" loading="lazy"><figcaption>img</figcaption></figure>
<p>解决方案：将前某层的结果做恒等映射到当前层</p>
